reviews.review_text: Black Dirt Live Again absolutely ferocious playing during Let it Grow. Thank you Betty Cantor Jackson for recording this amazing performance * Nick

Nice Show! Dig it! I'm endeavoring to bring some calm to my reviews.
Tis an exquisite recording and lovely performance!
I can recommend with a high degree of confidence.
Love the pace of the eyes, plenty of rooms for them all!
If I was to be as constrained as some in my review structures, I might call this one 4.25 for which there is no star rating system! And solid integers undervalue the nuance of the performance... but wtf~!
